title: The Mask: The Animated Series S02E19 - To Bee Or Not To Bee
description:
This was a request a long time ago, now I've got the chance to fill that gap.
One of the two missing episodes from the long known The Mask: TAS pack.
These episodes can be found on YouTube, but I thought I make it for the collectors.

The quality is good I think, the video source russian SATrip, and the audio source english TVrip.

Info:
Video: Divx 5, 704x528, 2000kbps
FPS: 25
Audio: English, MP3, 48000 kHz, 192kbps, stereo.

S02E26 "(The Angels Wanna Wear My) Green Mask" is coming soon too!

If you want, I can upload the whole series in this quality, but I warn you, my upload speed unfortunately is not the best. I'll try to seed this as much as I can, then upload S02E26.
Thank you for your patience, and enjoy this gem!
